name: NAPD 1
notes: Chron uses surface date (-30 BP), Ambrosia-rise (60 BP), and 2 radiocarbon dates. Ages are extrapolated below lowest radiocarbon date. Basal date is reasonable with respect to regional deglaciation (see Julig et al. 1990).
